column3: Black, Contemporary-style desk tape dispenser accommodates a 36-yard roll of tape up to 3/4 inch wide with an outside diameter of 2-1/2. The drum fits a roll with a 1" diameter core."
Plastic, handheld tape dispenser accommodates a 36-yard roll of tape up to 3/4 wide with a 1inch diameter core. Two mated halves separate to insert tape roll. Serrated cutting edge."
Transparent, 3/4 x 1,000 inch, Matte finish. Features a 1 inch core without dispenser. Made using quality 3M materials this tape is virtually invisible when applied. Ideal for mending documents.
Black, Page Yield: 42,000, This toner cartridge utilizes 37% post consumer recycled content by weight. The toner cartridge utilizes a new toner casing. For use in HP LaserJet 4250.
Black, Page Yield: 10000, Fits machine models HP Laser - LaserJet 5000 Series and 5100 Series printers.
